                {
                    "name": "Xill Eggs",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "The <a aonid=\"34\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">sickened</a> condition from xill eggs doesn't improve on its own until the disease is cured or runs its course. It can be cured with a 10-minute operation that requires a successful DC 26 <a aonid=\"9\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Medicine</a> check and deals 4d6 slashing damage to the host; <b>Saving Throw</b> DC 24 Fortitude; <b>Maximum Duration</b> 24 hours; <b>Stage 1</b> infested with no ill effect (8 hours); <b>Stage 2</b> sickened 1 (8 hours); <b>Stage 3</b> sickened 2 (4 hours); <b>Stage 4</b> sickened 2 and 2d6 <a aonid=\"29\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">persistent bleed damage</a> as larval xills burrow out of the body and immediately fade away into the <a aonid=\"9\" game-obj=\"Planes\">Ethereal Plane</a> (1 hour)",
